</paragraph>
<paragraph id="44F9C99DD7A06CF0AC6B2D699D6AB4D6" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
UNITED STATES. Arizona: Fort Valley, Coconino, on 
<taxonomicName id="B06BDFA2FF1061B1CD3C5B8C0A358569" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Pinus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Pinus ponderosa" order="Pinales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ponderosa">Pinus ponderosa</taxonomicName>
Laws., 21 September 1967, R. L. Gilbertson 7553 (holotype: ARIZ!, GenBank Acc. No. ITS: MK290732; isotype: SSMF 685-4578).
</paragraph>
